<title>rbnạ ynạdy yạ kl ạlʿbạd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rabũnạ yunạdẙ yạ kulã ạlʿibādi
 hạ ạlmsyḥu ạlfạdẙ yaṭlbu ạlkẖuṭạh
 ạirjiʿwạ ạlyhi wạmktẖwạ ldyhi
 taj̊nwạ min̊ yadyhi jidãẗa ạlḥyạh

[V2]
 ạlqrạr (hyạ llmsyḥ̊ ạ̉yhạ ạlbʿyd̊
 hạ tʿạl ḥạlạaⁿ tuṣ̊biḥan̊ saʿyd̊)2

[V3]
 2- yamnaḥu ạlrjạʾa yursilu ạlʿzạʾa
 yas̊kunu ạlsãmạʾa yasẖfaʿu lnạ̊
 hyãạ lạ tūảj̃l̊ ạ̉sriʿanã ạ̉qbl̊
 fy ạlṭryqi hll̊ qd kẖlãṣnā

[V4]
 3- ạdẖ̊habanã kẖab̃r̊ bạlḥyạẗi basẖ̃r̊
 lljmwʿi wạdẖ̊kur̊ ṣun̊ʿahu ạlʿajyb̊
 kam̊ hwa karymuⁿ qal̊buhu raḥymuⁿ
 ḥbuhu ʿaẓymuⁿ dwmaⁿạ yas̊tajyb̊</lyrics>
</song>